root: ^NOOO! My life's work! MY power! My... My... My... wow I actually feel really good now.
^Well would you look at that, a knock on the head really did the trick!
^It will take him a long time to regain my trust. I've got my eye on you, too Netrixi. Still without you, my father would still be utterly diablocial.
^What are we going to do about the stone? It is evil. We cannot leave it here. I can take it back to my village where it will be safe from the greedy hearts of the Iron Forge. No offense...
